18
00:01:08,500 --> 00:01:11,380
Angular momentum is, first of all, a vector quantity.

19
00:01:11,380 --> 00:01:13,400
It points in a direction.

20
00:01:13,400 --> 00:01:16,660
The mathematical definition of the angular momentum

21
00:01:16,660 --> 00:01:19,620
