35
00:01:48,760 --> 00:01:50,180
That's not something you prove.

36
00:01:50,180 --> 00:01:52,060
That's something you define,

37
00:01:52,060 --> 00:01:53,940
the direction of angular momentum.

38
00:01:54,780 --> 00:01:56,400
It's built up out of the

39
00:01:56,400 --> 00:01:58,020
mass, and the speed of rotation,

40
00:01:58,020 --> 00:02:00,020
