00:02:05,540 --> 00:02:06,740
the angular velocity.

44
00:02:08,900 --> 00:02:16,580
And any system, any ordinary system, composite system,

45
00:02:16,580 --> 00:02:21,100
this cup here, made up out of lots of atoms,

