550
00:25:00,980 --> 00:25:04,980
You can simultaneously measure them.

551
00:25:04,980 --> 00:25:05,980
Yeah, exactly.

552
00:25:05,980 --> 00:25:08,980
You can simultaneously measure them.

553
00:25:08,980 --> 00:25:10,980
What if they don't commute?

554
00:25:10,980 --> 00:25:13,980
Then you can't simultaneously measure them.

555
00:25:13,980 --> 00:25:15,980
The most famous example of two things

556
00:25:15,980 --> 00:25:17,980
that you cannot simultaneously measure,

557
00:25:17,980 --> 00:25:19,980
